  <data name="lblMessage.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Recycling is not just about sorting waste ,it's about reshaping our future.
Every bottle, can, or piece of paper you save from the trash is a small victory for the planet.
One person's habit becomes a community's culture, and that culture can heal the Earth. </value>
